1
00:00:00,170 --> 00:00:02,040
Oh, Morimoto...

2
00:00:02,040 --> 00:00:04,460
Did you just get here too?

3
00:00:04,460 --> 00:00:06,800
He's a quick learner for a rookie.

4
00:00:06,800 --> 00:00:09,930
Calling him by his last name is so formal.

5
00:00:09,930 --> 00:00:11,720
He doesn't really look like a Morimoto, does he?

6
00:00:11,720 --> 00:00:13,510
What is a Morimoto supposed to look like anyway?

7
00:00:13,510 --> 00:00:14,140
Haha.

8
00:00:14,140 --> 00:00:16,020
He's really good-looking, though.

9
00:00:16,020 --> 00:00:17,270
And so tall, too.

10
00:00:17,270 --> 00:00:18,770
Did you ever want to be a model?

11
00:00:18,770 --> 00:00:20,940
No, I've always wanted to be a makeup artist.

12
00:00:20,940 --> 00:00:22,440
That's such a waste.

13
00:00:22,440 --> 00:00:25,070
You should show him off more.

14
00:00:25,070 --> 00:00:28,450
How about starting with some PR photos for the company?

15
00:00:28,450 --> 00:00:29,820
That's a great idea!

16
00:00:29,820 --> 00:00:32,990
We actually need to recruit new people on social media.

17
00:00:33,450 --> 00:00:35,370
It'd be perfect if you did the shoot.

18
00:00:35,370 --> 00:00:37,290
No, really, that's okay.

19
00:00:37,290 --> 00:00:39,620
If today's shoot
ends early...

20
00:00:39,620 --> 00:00:41,040
Why don't we just shoot it here?

21
00:00:41,040 --> 00:00:43,080
No, I'd feel too self-conscious.

22
00:00:43,080 --> 00:00:45,550
Don't be shy.
You've been a huge help to us.

23
00:00:45,550 --> 00:00:46,670
Really?

24
00:00:46,670 --> 00:00:49,380
- But this is so sudden...
- It'll be fine, really.

25
00:00:49,380 --> 00:00:52,590
(Oh no, things are moving way too fast.)

26
00:00:52,930 --> 00:00:54,430
(It's really hard to say no in this atmosphere.)

27
00:00:54,430 --> 00:00:57,140
- Good work today.
- Thanks for your hard work.
